description:
Alex M.O.R.P.H. - Prime Mover (The Remixes) (2013) 

                   Trance | Armada Music Bundles / Alex M.O.R.P.H.

             320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2013-07-26 | 02:29:23 | 349 Mb





The summer of 2012 saw Alex M.O.R.P.H. swift into the next gear. The charismatic trance DJ and producer, favoured for his many quality productions, stellar remixes and energetic drive, kicked in with 'Prime Mover', his second artist album. A set of 17 originals, travelling the global clubs and arena's to this day. 'Prime Mover' now takes a rebound, with the official Remixes album! Including remixes by renowned names and rising talents, 'Prime Mover (The Remixes)' brings the brand new interpretations of tracks like 'An Angel's Love', 'Monday Morning Madness', 'Waking Up The Stars' and more, remixed by Andrew Rayel, Shogun, Skytech, KhoMha, Alexander Popov and many more! Bringing out a vivid new painting of the smash that is 'Prime Mover', this remix collection will surely colour your night and day.
